OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'We cut back on energy but 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Four direct debits trebled' 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Amy Appleyard had been paying #136 a   
OL,6, month to heat and light her home.      
OL,8,FKnowing that energy bills would rise in
OL,9,Fthe autumn, she and her family had cut 
OL,10,Fback on how much power they were using.
OL,12,FBut they were shocked to be told that  
OL,13,Ftheir monthly direct debit would rise  
OL,14,Fmore than three times to #442.         
OL,16,FThey are just one of many UK households
OL,17,Fwho have cut back on energy but are    
OL,18,Fstill being charged higher direct      
OL,19,Fdebits. But suppliers say bills have to
OL,20,Freflect soaring energy prices.         
